1989 — Sharp SM83 (LR35902)

Almost compatible extension of the Intel 8080 and Zilog Z80, used as the CPU in the Nintendo GameBoy, it changed a few instructions and added some others.

Address space
16-bit
7 6 5 4 3 2 1 0 0
F Z N H C 0 0 0 0 IE IE

Main table

  • Green marks new instructions to the Zilog Z80.
  • Red marks new instructions replacing earlier ones for the Zilog Z80.
  • Orange marks instructions present but undocumented in Zilog Z80 and documented for the Sharp SM83 (LR35902).
  • Pink background marks undocumented instructions.
  • Plum background marks duplicate instructions.
